channel.description:

I did that and now it still doesn't work so do i need to download jdk 6? for it to work i know you need jdk 6 for allot of the private server clients so if you could please tell me where to download jdk 6 (please provide a link) and tell me witch one to download to get clients to work there is like jdku and other versions and im not sure witch on to get and how to fix the red x in the corner it would be appreciated
I'm sorry if this broke any rules i read all the stickies and i don't think this does i am extremely sorry if it does but please try to answer my questions
